descr: "A text description of the DICOM SOP instances selected in the ImagingManifest; or the reason for, or significance of, the selection."

fields.name: uid
fields.descr: "Study instance UID of the SOP instances in the selection."

fields.name: imagingStudy
fields.descr: "Reference to the Imaging Study in FHIR form."

fields.name: endpoint
fields.descr: "The network service providing access (e.g., query, view, or retrieval) for the study. See implementation notes for information about using DICOM endpoints. A study-level endpoint applies to each series in the study, unless overridden by a series-level endpoint with the same Endpoint.type."

fields.name: series
fields.descr: "Series identity and locating information of the DICOM SOP instances in the selection."
